{"tid":1544870,"cid":31,"subCid":9,"title":"順安邨連儂牆","createTime":"2019-09-05T16:57:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-26T23:12:33.000Z","uid":317429,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"04619cc69148132ba0c14977780b28ba1272e391","tid":1544870,"uid":317429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T16:57:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XvU1U0x.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXvU1U0x.jpg&h=18787c11&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n尋日食完飯落街行行下俾我見到依張咁嘅嘢<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>我撕左佢</strong></span><br />\n跟住我谷鬼氣<br />\n去咗順利邨印咗幾張文宣<br />\n貼左一張文宣係同一個位<br />\n唔知而家仲喺唔喺度 <br />\n（冇去睇 我估已經比啲廢老撕咗）<br />\n希望各位住附近嘅巴打<br />\n可以一齊整<br />\n<strong>係順安去順利條天橋嘅籃球場個度</strong><br />\n唔想變咗<span style=\"color: blue;\">藍C連儂牆</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>大家一齊光復四順</strong></span>"},{"pid":"8617cade71ecfc2ce9ba64d8b3a39c0332c7ddd1","tid":1544870,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T16:57:17.000Z","msg":"[行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/reLz9Yb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FreLz9Yb.jpg&h=bc5ea362&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VeJJ3id.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVeJJ3id.jpg&h=50bde3c1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"230ba9271fc806f6b7bca96e8a17a9df1696e7f3","tid":1544870,"uid":117906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T16:57:56.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">撤LLM 對準政權</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3E7OjKb.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3E7OjKb.gif&h=66b4ea40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uZFWW8o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuZFWW8o.jpg&h=4196affc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zNutjAi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzNutjAi.jpg&h=1817afe5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">得到黨媒認證</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sELTeyX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsELTeyX.png&h=0e8c0efe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">#Chinazi旗係一個符號，不斷向世界輸出反共思想！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">#Chinazi 赤納粹</span></span></strong><br />\nChinazi就係China+Nazi。<br />\n赤=共產紅色恐怖, 納粹不解釋。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"> 全民反共 對準政權！</span></span></strong><br />\n黑警、黨鐵，港共全部都係人民既敵人<br />\n而背後一直有一個終極大Boss中共<br />\n<br />\n呢一刻中共絕對係十個煲得兩個蓋，準備爆煲。<br />\n今日唔號召世界圍堵中共，更待何時？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">用#Chinazi黎connect全世界</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">1. Connect所有黃絲。</span></strong><br />\n殘酷既現實係，並唔係所有黃絲都支持勇武。但黃絲最驚就係共產黨打到黎，一於用反共connect呢班淺黃!<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">2. Connect部分中立/藍絲。</span></strong><br />\n中立/藍絲既上一輩，全部都係親身經歷過六四既年代，唔少甚至係大陸生活過。係大陸生活上所面對既不公義、中共點砌人生豬肉、佢地可能比我地感受更深。佢地唔會否認對共產黨既恐懼！一齊黎喚醒佢地對中共既不信任！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">3. Connect全世界</span></strong><br />\nNazi既惡行到今時今日都依然係全世界既傷口，但佢地未必注意到係21世紀有個同Nazi不遑多讓既Chinazi！用#chinazi旗加海量文宣，話比佢地知我地既共同敵人係中共！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>目標：全香港市民都知到呢個符號！<br />\n請大家用各種創意方法令大家知道呢道Chinazi旗！<br />\n記住！存在即勝利！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">雙手奉上</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/09/02/9dojRG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F09%2F02%2F9dojRG.png&h=baf47345&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JXMrzU3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJXMrzU3.jpg&h=4fd76574&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8fa876882c6700d7fb4a6bfbbdee7430071dcce9","tid":1544870,"uid":210165,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T16:58:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8c609da838719f6f2790c5d5236cf31c4c7a9959","tid":1544870,"uid":210165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T16:59:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"507605e3027e08f2ba644795297da4e916722903","tid":1544870,"uid":317429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8fa876882c6700d7fb4a6bfbbdee7430071dcce9","tid":1544870,"uid":210165,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T16:58:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T17:00:37.000Z","msg":"你講得啱 吾應該撕<br />\n所以一定要搵多啲手足一齊貼爆佢"},{"pid":"b7981b1c1c541fbe916fc429c1719f9a6b17d2dd","tid":1544870,"uid":317429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8c609da838719f6f2790c5d5236cf31c4c7a9959","tid":1544870,"uid":210165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8fa876882c6700d7fb4a6bfbbdee7430071dcce9","tid":1544870,"uid":210165,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T16:58:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T16:59:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T17:03:23.000Z","msg":"My bad"},{"pid":"a6d35081e669cfa49640ea6bbe6106a7d94db2da","tid":1544870,"uid":176903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T15:57:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/p